<br>
But, and there is always a but, the Chinese are not iraq or afghanistan. Even though China is one of the world's biggest human rights violators they are still a country in the legit, they are a permanent member of the UN security council, and they are a country armed with nuclear weapons, advanced military technology (thx USA), and an army that is immense in its magnitude. And with 1.2 billion people living there, they have the means to have their army grow almost exponentially. <br>
<br>
